    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game Concept</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <strong>Bubumbu</strong>, you will help walking puzzle pieces explore various worlds in search of the place they belong. The object portrayed on the puzzle pieces gives a hint to where they may fit. The interaction and logic reminds a lot of point-and-click adventures, and the challenge similar that of a hidden objects game. The total playtime is about 30 minutes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303420/extras/244e133844e92af5cd0e0e41eb90294f.poster.avif?t=1741347427\" width=416 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303420/extras/244e133844e92af5cd0e0e41eb90294f.webm?t=1741347427\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303420/extras/244e133844e92af5cd0e0e41eb90294f.mp4?t=1741347427\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Secrets All Around</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In addition to the main puzzle mechanics, the game worlds also contain hidden things around the environment. By pressing certain details you spot in your surroundings you may discover these secrets - and then they will show up in your &quot;Island of Secrets&quot;.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303420/extras/e85469d15c6ca9fcf758b6241fa52d4b.poster.avif?t=1741347427\" width=434 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303420/extras/e85469d15c6ca9fcf758b6241fa52d4b.webm?t=1741347427\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303420/extras/e85469d15c6ca9fcf758b6241fa52d4b.mp4?t=1741347427\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
